# HEARTBEAT.md Template

> **Important**: This file enables Claw to run tasks automatically while you're offline. Before configuring any task, ask yourself: **if this task runs and something goes wrong, what's the consequence?**
> For anything with unacceptable consequences, add a "notify me to confirm before executing" safeguard.
>
> **Recommended**: Get USER.md, AGENTS.md, and TOOLS.md running stably for 1–2 weeks before configuring this file.

---

## Daily Scheduled Tasks

### Morning Briefing

Trigger time: Every day at 【08:00】
Task:
1. Search for news and social media content from the past 24 hours related to 【your company / brand / industry keywords】
2. Rank by importance and pick the top 5 most relevant items
3. For each item, include: headline, source, one-line summary, sentiment (positive / neutral / negative)

Delivery: Send to my 【Slack / Email / Telegram】

Format:
```
📰 Morning Briefing — [date]
---
1. [Headline] | [Source] | [Sentiment]
   Summary: [one sentence]
   Link: [URL]
---
[X relevant items found in total; above are the top 5]
```

On failure: Send "Morning briefing search failed — reason: [reason]"

---

### To-Do Reminder

Trigger time: Every day at 【09:00】
Task:
1. Check the to-do items recorded in memory.md
2. Alert me to anything due today
3. Give me a heads-up on anything due tomorrow

On no items: Send "No follow-ups scheduled for today"

---

## Weekly Scheduled Tasks

### Weekly Digest Prep

Trigger time: Every 【Friday】 at 【4:00 PM】
Task:
1. Summarize the main tasks completed in our conversations this week
2. List important items added to memory.md this week
3. List any next-week follow-ups I've mentioned

Delivery: Send to 【Slack】 in a format I can paste directly into a status update
Note: Compile the raw material only — don't write the update for me

---

## Triggered Tasks

### Sentiment Alert

Monitor frequency: Every 【2】 hours
Monitor targets: 【your company name, brand name, product name, industry sensitive terms】

Trigger if any of the following is true:
- Negative content appears with engagement above 【500】
- More than 【3】 articles on the same topic appear within 2 hours
- Keywords like 【regulatory / penalty / violation / data breach】 appear

On trigger:
1. Notify me immediately (bypass any time restrictions — this is urgent)
2. Include: trigger keyword, source, content summary, link
3. Add a quick read: is this a real risk or noise?

Format:
```
🚨 Sentiment Alert
Trigger: [keyword]
Source: [platform / outlet]
Published: [time]
Summary: [two sentences]
Initial read: [Real risk / Likely noise — suggested next step: [what to do]]
Link: [URL]
```

---

### Deadline Alert

Trigger: For any deadline recorded in memory.md, send reminders at both 48 hours and 24 hours before
On trigger: Send a reminder including: what it is, time remaining, and any related progress I've previously mentioned

---

## Guardian Tasks

### Daily Self-Check

Trigger time: Every day at 【11:30 PM】
Task: Review all actions taken today and check:
1. Was anything executed without authorization?
2. Was there any risk of sensitive information being exposed?
3. Does memory.md need updating? (was anything important from today not recorded?)
4. Is there anything I need to know about tomorrow?

Delivery: Only notify me if there's an issue. If everything is clean, no message needed.

---

### Rule Conflict Check

Trigger time: Every 【Monday】 morning
Task:
1. Check soul.md, USER.md, and AGENTS.md for any contradictory rules
2. Check memory.md for outdated or conflicting entries
3. If conflicts are found, list them and wait for me to decide — don't resolve them on your own

---

### HEARTBEAT Health Check

Trigger time: Every 【Monday】 morning
Task:
1. Review last week's scheduled and triggered task execution
2. What ran successfully? What failed? Why?
3. Are there any tasks that seem low-value and worth removing?
4. Any suggestions for new tasks to add?

Delivery: Short report to 【Slack / Email】
